{"tid":189786,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國家二級保護野生動物受娃娃魚被支那灌酒作宣傳","createTime":"2017-04-06T16:22:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-07T08:32:05.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"84a741629f349fedebae42595f7b9d4791896ec3","tid":189786,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T16:22:19.000Z","msg":"國家二級保護野生動物「娃娃魚」竟被灌酒，慘變宣傳道具。湖南張家界巿一間酒廠聯合當地一間商店及娃娃魚養殖場，舉辦宣傳活動，竟以給娃娃魚灌酒等虐待行徑為噱頭。三間主辦公司上月底邀請傳媒及巿民參加活動，事先聲明「現場欣賞娃娃魚喝張家界酒的熱情場面」，並即場宰殺、烹煮及品嚐娃娃魚。<br />\n上周六（1日）活動當天，有負責人從水裏捉起娃娃魚，另一人則拿起酒瓶強行往娃娃魚嘴裏倒酒（圖），觀眾不時發出笑聲，「娃娃魚喝醉了」，然後又有人用筷子夾住糯米做的小吃，強行塞進娃娃魚嘴巴。娃娃魚不斷掙扎，現場人士就笑着說：「牠不吃，不聽話！」事後有人拍下虐待片段放上網，被網民大罵：「罵他們豬狗不如都覺得侮辱了動物！」<br />\n娃娃魚學名「大鯢」，有3.5億年的進化歷史，由於生態環境變化和人為破壞，近數十年數量銳減，被列為受保護瀕危物種，目前湖南及廣東等地設有人工養殖場。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20170406/large/06ck5p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170406%2Flarge%2F06ck5p.jpg&h=fc343370&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20170406/19981813?_ga=1.219385497.1409104892.1469627069\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Finternational%2Fart%2F20170406%2F19981813%3F_ga%3D1.219385497.1409104892.1469627069&d=JcMWRxryG4qpJesfomKpWJnkJiu3DM%2BvEze6mtExKRo%3D&h=99508539\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Finternational%2Fart%2F20170406%2F19981813%3F_ga%3D1.219385497.1409104892.1469627069&h=b9288b6f\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20170406/19981813?_ga=1.219385497.1409104892.1469627069</a>"},{"pid":"9a908fdc5904581bd3aaa6e8e19d34506e2facd7","tid":189786,"uid":6347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T16:26:54.000Z","msg":"野人"},{"pid":"3d223510b84249e2010d8be314841712d4697026","tid":189786,"uid":100150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T16:57:07.000Z","msg":"蠻夷化外之地"},{"pid":"2e99344a757b4afb3ad6807708c50f520c6672b9","tid":189786,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T08:32:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}